MKMVA spokesperson Carl Niehaus has been suspended from the ANC with immediate effect for bringing the party into disrepute. JOHANNESBURG - MKMVA spokesperson Carl Niehaus has been suspended from the ANC with immediate effect for bringing the party into disrepute. Niehaus received a letter signed by the deputy secretary-general of the ANC Jessie Duarte. READ: Deadline for Zuma's arrest looming He says he'll be appealing his suspension.